# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1390
translate spanish swistun_09c1bc54:

    # ka "Yes. Everything’s very simple."
    ka "Sí. Todo es muy simple."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1396
translate spanish swistun_e8d20309:

    # ka "Kill him. Then taste just one piece of his flesh."
    ka "matarlo. Luego saborea solo una pieza de su carne."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1397
translate spanish swistun_7f3e153c:

    # ka "You can't even imagine how delicious his chakra will be..."
    ka "Ni siquiera puedes imaginar lo delicioso que será su chakra..."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1398
translate spanish swistun_d44d6241:

    # ka "And your abilities will develop much quicker."
    ka "Y tus habilidades se desarrollarán mucho más rápido."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1400
translate spanish swistun_cd5147a8:

    # r "Jeesus... Kamiko... I... I don't kill people..."
    r "Jeesus... Kamiko... Yo... no mato a personas..."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1402
translate spanish swistun_e8ef3723:

    # ka "You'll have to."
    ka "Usted tendrá que hacerlo."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1403
translate spanish swistun_6ebf2160:

    # ka "Do you remember what we talked about before your transformation?"
    ka "¿Recuerdas de lo que hablamos antes de tu transformación?"

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1404
translate spanish swistun_6c0feba4:

    # ka "This world is much crueler than you might think."
    ka "Este mundo es mucho más cruel de lo que usted podría pensar."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1405
translate spanish swistun_6b76fbc7:

    # ka "Don't worry, you're no longer just a person, there's power inside you... You're an Ōtsutsuki, although you don't realize it yet."
    ka "No te preocupes, ya no eres solo una persona, hay poder dentro de ti... Eres un O-tsutsuki, aunque aún no te das cuenta de ello."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1407
translate spanish swistun_051f1bcf:

    # r "Am I the same... Just like you?"
    r "¿Soy lo mismo... ¿Al igual que tú?"

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1409
translate spanish swistun_bb1808e8:

    # ka "My precious child, I have nurtured you all this time, you are just like me."
    ka "Mi precioso niño, te he criado todo este tiempo, eres igual que yo."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1411
translate spanish swistun_cf2d991a:

    # r "Even if... Could you maybe do it yourself? And then I will taste... Him..."
    r "Incluso si... ¿Podrías hacerlo tú mismo? Y entonces tendré un gusto... É..."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1413
translate spanish swistun_311f23ec:

    # ka "I can't. This is your sacrifice. Yes, I prepared it for you. But it's all yours."
    ka "No puedo. Este es su sacrificio. Sí, lo preparé para ti. Pero todo es tuyo."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1414
translate spanish swistun_8eaf4ef7:

    # ka "I...I am a beast. We hunt for chakra and feed on it alone, that is what gives us strength."
    ka "Yo... Soy una bestia. Buscamos chakra y nos alimentamos de ella sola, eso es lo que nos da fuerza."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1416
translate spanish swistun_38e43538:

    # r "So... I have to... Do it alone..."
    r "Así que... tengo que... Hazlo solo..."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1418
translate spanish swistun_162e2206:

    # ka "I'll leave you a sharp knife. That will be enough."
    ka "te dejaré un cuchillo afilado. Eso será suficiente."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1419
translate spanish swistun_9a4464ef:

    # ka "You don't have to rush, do it before nightfall. As soon as you taste his flesh and feel a surge of strength... Anyway, you will understand."
    ka "Usted no tiene que apresurarse, hacerlo antes de caer la noche. Tan pronto como usted saborea su carne y siente una oleada de fuerza ... De todos modos, usted comprenderá."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1420
translate spanish swistun_8cefb69f:

    # ka "And remember."
    ka "y recuerda."

# game/kuremiraywayo.rpy:1421
translate spanish swistun_a528fb3d:

    # ka "No pity for food."
    ka "No hay pena por la comida."

